  "format": "Sean Fennessey and Chris Ryan review Fede Alvarez's 'Alien: Romulus,' rank all nine 'Alien' films, and Sean sits down with Alvarez to talk practical sets, the fourth act, and the Rook decision.",
  "segments": [
